    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "Blb6L",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 3960,
      "name": "Animation-Annotations",
      "width": 360,
      "height": 280,
      "content": "动画规格 (Animation Specs)\n\n• Tab 切换: 380ms ease-out\n  内容区域淡入淡出 + 轻微滑移\n\n• 卡片入场: 360ms spring\n  从 opacity:0, translateY:12px 进入\n  spring(1, 80, 10) 缓动函数\n\n• 输入框聚焦: 200ms ease\n  边框颜色过渡\n\n• 错误状态: 280ms ease-out\n  红色边框 + 错误消息滑入\n\n• Reduced Motion 回退:\n  prefers-reduced-motion: reduce\n  禁用所有位移动画\n  仅保留 opacity 过渡 (150ms)"
    },
